  Golf in France  
France has over 650 courses, set among some of the world's finest scenery. Not to mention the food & wine, and half price golf! 
 
 
   
  
  Lisbon Golf Coast   
A delightful region with excellent yet fairly quiet courses, cheap golf, fine beaches and the sunny blue skies of Portugal. 
 
  
  
 
